ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The course to take if interested in nondomination. Yes, it's a central theme in contemporary political theory.

I will strongly recommend this course to another student simply because the course material is quite strong. We grapple with a matter of clear relevance and importance at all levels of analysis. Last, and not the least, Professor Shapiro is an extremely gifted teacher and it is a joy to sit in his class.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It deepens my understanding of nondomination from many facets. It helps my research on it greatly.
